escorting you, Count.

119
00:05:35,510 --> 00:05:37,800
Young Master. What’s wrong?

120
00:05:40,750 --> 00:05:43,390
By the way, what did you say to them

121
00:05:43,480 --> 00:05:44,600
about Baroness Ban’s mischief
last night?

122
00:05:46,920 --> 00:05:47,950
