that I lost my manner.

130
00:06:06,160 --> 00:06:07,070
But, Young Master,

131
00:06:07,390 --> 00:06:09,240
the people we sent out

132
00:06:09,360 --> 00:06:10,510
all have made progress lately,

133
00:06:11,600 --> 00:06:12,430
and they are doing well,

134
00:06:13,160 --> 00:06:15,190
while here, we have made
no progress at all.

135
00:06:16,870 --> 00:06:17,800
You are right.

136
00:06:18,510 --> 00:06:19,480
It’s time.

137
00:06:20,060 --> 00:06:26,020
<i>Rong’s Mansion</i>

138
00:06:26,680 --> 00:06:27,390
Du Jiu.

139
00:06:28,720 --> 00:06:30,160
Now that you’re aware of
your misbehavior last night,

140
00:06:30,560 --> 00:06:31,510
I need you

141
00:06:31,750 --> 00:06:33,430
to go pick some jewelry and toys

142
00:06:33,920 --> 00:06:36,040
and deliver them to Baroness Ban

143
00:06:36,430 --> 00:06:37,430
