for her arrangement last night

144
00:06:37,560 --> 00:06:38,390
and apology as well.

145
00:06:39,600 --> 00:06:40,360
Young Master…

146
00:06:41,000 --> 00:06:41,430
I…

147
00:06:41,740 --> 00:06:44,180
<i>Rong’s Mansion</i>

148
00:06:45,270 --> 00:06:46,510
What did I do wrong this time?

149
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:50,720
Why should I apologize for nothing?

150
00:06:59,360 --> 00:07:00,070
Hey,

151
00:07:00,510 --> 00:07:01,920
I’ve been waiting here for two hours.

152
00:07:02,160 --> 00:07:03,830
Tell me,
will Baroness see me or not?

153
00:07:07,630 --> 00:07:10,680
Last night, you insulted us
by saying that

154
00:07:10,800 --> 00:07:11,950
we couldn’t do anything but play.

155
00:07:12,310 --> 00:07:14,190
Now, are you complaining that

156
00:07:14,190 --> 00:07:15,070
I’ve kept you waiting?

157
00:07:17,040 --> 00:07:18,240
Please don’t be mad.

158
00:07:18,310 --> 00:07:19,480
It was my fault indeed.

159
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:22,120
But today, His Grace sent me here

160
00:07:22,630 --> 00:07:24,040
to deliver a gift

161
00:07:24,310 --> 00:07:25,190
and some words

162
00:07:25,270 --> 00:07:26,480
to say to Baroness Ban face to face.

163
00:07:27,270 --> 00:07:28,480
So, please inform her.

164
00:07:30,920 --> 00:07:33,000
Baroness went out this morning.

165
00:07:33,070 --> 00:07:34,040
You can come later.

166
00:07:34,270 --> 00:07:36,510
Went out?
Why didn’t you tell me earlier?

167
00:07:36,510 --> 00:07:38,240
Because I didn’t want to.

168
00:07:39,120 --> 00:07:40,950
If you don’t like it,
just complain to your master.

169
00:07:41,120 --> 00:07:42,600
Don’t get me mad, or I…

170
00:07:43,950 --> 00:07:44,750
You what?

171
00:07:46,120 --> 00:07:48,270
Don’t try to scare me.
I’ll come another day.

172
00:07:48,270 --> 00:07:49,000
I’ll leave the gift here.

173
00:07:49,000 --> 00:07:49,720
Stop.

174
00:07:52,240 --> 00:07:53,480
Baroness asked me

175
00:07:53,480 --> 00:07:55,190
to let you deliver this to Count Rong.

176
00:07:55,190 --> 00:07:56,800
She’s going to give a banquet
in the suburbs.

177
00:07:56,950 --> 00:07:58,070
