178
00:08:01,070 --> 00:08:02,750
Don’t be smug. I’ll deal with you later.

179
00:08:04,750 --> 00:08:05,870
What’s the big deal?

180
00:08:25,070 --> 00:08:25,920
That Baroness Ban

181
00:08:25,920 --> 00:08:27,270
found such a remote place.

182
00:08:27,720 --> 00:08:29,160
God knows what she’s up to.

183
00:08:29,800 --> 00:08:31,630
Young Master, we’d better leave.

184
00:08:32,600 --> 00:08:34,560
Maybe she wants to revenge

185
00:08:34,750 --> 00:08:35,950
for what happened last night.

186
00:08:37,440 --> 00:08:39,120
She can be wilful sometimes,

187
00:08:39,720 --> 00:08:41,320
but she’s a decent person after all.

188
00:08:41,870 --> 00:08:42,840
She won’t mess around.

189
00:08:54,390 --> 00:08:56,390
Young Master, I’ll go
decline her invitation.

190
00:08:57,120 --> 00:08:57,790
No.

191
00:08:58,750 --> 00:08:59,630
Since I agreed to come,

192
00:09:00,080 --> 00:09:01,360
I should keep my word.

193
00:09:01,480 --> 00:09:02,320
But Young Master,

194
00:09:02,480 --> 00:09:04,030
people in our mansion all know that
you don’t skate.

195
00:09:04,600 --> 00:09:06,030
Even the winter ice in the yard

196
00:09:06,120 --> 00:09:07,080
must be broken.

197
00:09:07,390 --> 00:09:08,720
Why do you have to suffer from this?

198
00:09:13,030 --> 00:09:14,600
I decided to be friendly with the Bans.

199
00:09:14,670 --> 00:09:15,790
How can I break my promise?

200
00:09:17,390 --> 00:09:18,080
Well…

201
00:09:29,390 --> 00:09:30,000
Here they are.

202
00:09:34,840 --> 00:09:35,910
He did show up.

203
00:09:36,320 --> 00:09:38,360
Xie Wanyu didn’t lie to me.

204
00:09:48,840 --> 00:09:51,960
Count Rong, I didn’t think you’d come.

205
00:09:55,000 --> 00:09:56,320
With your great hospitality,

206
00:09:56,670 --> 00:09:58,000
