210
00:10:24,120 --> 00:10:25,840
Thanks a lot. I love it.

211
00:10:29,630 --> 00:10:31,870
Young Master, I just randomly picked it.

212
00:10:32,360 --> 00:10:33,480
I didn’t expect this.

213
00:10:46,600 --> 00:10:48,080
The scenery in the mountains is good.

214
00:10:48,750 --> 00:10:50,440
And autumn is a good season to go out.

215
00:10:51,080 --> 00:10:52,390
Now, the elaborate arrangements
from Baroness Ban

216
00:10:52,600 --> 00:10:53,790
