220
00:11:02,150 --> 00:11:03,510
but I’m good at having fun.

221
00:11:04,000 --> 00:11:05,200
Now you are here,

222
00:11:05,480 --> 00:11:06,910
I guarantee that

223
00:11:07,120 --> 00:11:08,670
