276
00:15:19,910 --> 00:15:21,200
I dare not compete with you.

277
00:15:22,550 --> 00:15:24,240
Skating alone would be boring.

278
00:15:24,630 --> 00:15:25,440
It’s a pity

279
00:15:26,030 --> 00:15:27,790
that winter hasn’t come.

280
00:15:28,200 --> 00:15:28,960
Or it would be

281
00:15:29,030 --> 00:15:31,670
more fun to have a snowball fight
while skating.

282
00:15:37,910 --> 00:15:38,960
I scored a point.

283
00:15:51,960 --> 00:15:53,360
Two points, Count!

284
00:15:53,550 --> 00:15:54,600
Catch up with me!

285
00:16:10,200 --> 00:16:11,200
Baroness, watch out!

286
00:16:32,480 --> 00:16:35,000
Please forgive me, Baroness.

287
00:16:36,120 --> 00:16:37,000
Never mind.

288
00:16:39,910 --> 00:16:41,390
Thanks for your help.

289
00:16:48,270 --> 00:16:49,000
Count.

290
00:16:50,120 --> 00:16:51,440
It looks that

291
00:16:51,720 --> 00:16:53,390
you’re not really good at skating.

292
00:16:56,960 --> 00:16:57,790
It’s my fault

293
00:16:58,120 --> 00:16:59,720
that I mistook you.

294
00:17:00,360 --> 00:17:01,480
Don’t blame yourself.

295
00:17:01,870 --> 00:17:03,360
I do like skating.

296
00:17:03,720 --> 00:17:05,790
However, that’s when I was a kid.

297
00:17:06,000 --> 00:17:08,080
I haven’t done this for long.
I’m a little rusty.

298
00:17:09,110 --> 00:17:10,200
I see.

299
00:17:11,350 --> 00:17:13,680
Count, you’re knowledgeable

300
00:17:13,920 --> 00:17:14,830
but

301
00:17:14,830 --> 00:17:16,480
when it comes to playing,

302
00:17:16,480 --> 00:17:17,440
I’m better than you.

303
00:17:17,880 --> 00:17:18,720
How about

304
00:17:19,000 --> 00:17:20,200
letting me teach you to skate?

305
00:17:22,640 --> 00:17:23,880
I’m afraid it’s hard for me

306
00:17:23,920 --> 00:17:25,110
and it would take much time.

307
00:17:25,310 --> 00:17:27,350
It’s not hard at all. I’ll teach you.

308
00:17:29,640 --> 00:17:30,440
Then…

309
00:17:32,640 --> 00:17:33,960
I should say thank…

310
00:17:39,720 --> 00:17:40,480
Count Cheng’an,

311
00:17:41,030 --> 00:17:42,790
you should watch the way
you stand on the ice.

312
00:17:44,160 --> 00:17:44,920
See?

313
00:17:45,880 --> 00:17:48,310
Get the skates into the ice
and you won’t fall.

314
00:17:50,480 --> 00:17:51,510
Thank you, Baroness.

315
00:17:53,200 --> 00:17:54,030
Give me your hands.

316
00:17:57,880 --> 00:17:58,790
I’ll lead you.

317
00:17:59,880 --> 00:18:00,720
Wait, Baroness.

318
00:18:02,270 --> 00:18:03,790
Don’t worry. I’m here with you.

319
00:18:05,110 --> 00:18:05,680
Let’s go.

320
00:18:18,680 --> 00:18:22,270
♪The drizzle is falling on the ground♪

321
00:18:22,270 --> 00:18:26,310
♪Love is growing in the heart♪

322
00:18:26,480 --> 00:18:30,240
♪Can’t let those honeyed words stay♪

323
00:18:30,240 --> 00:18:33,030
♪Wait for him day and night♪

324
00:18:34,270 --> 00:18:38,000
♪Meteors shoot across the evening glow♪

325
00:18:38,240 --> 00:18:42,030
♪Her smile is like the beautiful painting
in my memory♪

326
00:18:42,240 --> 00:18:46,000
♪Pick a flower that will never fade♪

327
00:18:46,000 --> 00:18:49,200
♪And give it to the girl in my dream♪

328
00:18:50,070 --> 00:18:53,830
♪Wait for the sunny weather
when we first met♪

329
00:18:54,030 --> 00:18:57,310
♪We know time will give the answer♪

330
00:18:57,310 --> 00:18:58,830
♪Search for the girl in my memory♪

331
00:18:58,880 --> 00:18:59,960
♪That boy♪

332
00:18:59,960 --> 00:19:00,920
♪Loves that girl♪

333
00:19:00,920 --> 00:19:02,000
♪Loves her hair♪

334
00:19:02,000 --> 00:19:04,880
♪Loves her dress♪

335
00:19:05,750 --> 00:19:09,680
♪Wait for the sunny weather quietly♪

336
00:19:10,200 --> 00:19:12,510
Come on, brother. Let’s skate together.

337
00:19:12,510 --> 00:19:13,720
-It’ll be fun.
-Brother!

338
00:19:13,960 --> 00:19:16,070
Brother, I can’t.

339
00:19:16,350 --> 00:19:17,400
I’m scared.

340
00:19:18,270 --> 00:19:20,310
Don’t worry. I’ll be with you.

341
00:19:20,310 --> 00:19:21,670
Come on, give me your hands.

342
00:19:22,480 --> 00:19:23,790
Come. Slowly.

343
00:19:25,830 --> 00:19:27,270
You can skate, see?

344
00:19:37,550 --> 00:19:38,110
Count.

345
00:19:38,920 --> 00:19:40,000
You’re actually gifted.

346
00:19:40,480 --> 00:19:43,000
Then… It’s on your own.

347
00:19:44,880 --> 00:19:45,480
Go.

348
00:19:56,830 --> 00:19:57,750
Believe in yourself.

349
00:19:57,920 --> 00:19:58,640
You can do it.

350
00:20:29,070 --> 00:20:30,960
You look even better when you smile.

351
00:20:43,440 --> 00:20:45,160
Baroness, please don’t mind it.

352
00:20:45,880 --> 00:20:47,920
Now we are tied.

353
00:20:49,000 --> 00:20:50,590
You are a fast learner.

354
00:20:51,640 --> 00:20:52,720
But Count Cheng’an,

355
00:20:52,960 --> 00:20:55,350
you’ll have a long way to go to beat me.

356
00:21:03,550 --> 00:21:04,590
Don’t worry about him.

357
00:21:09,240 --> 00:21:10,440
He’s good at skating.

358
00:21:25,440 --> 00:21:27,030
The ice is thin there.
Be careful, Count.

359
00:21:55,680 --> 00:21:57,400
Count Xie’s daughter, Xie Wanyu,

360
00:21:57,790 --> 00:22:00,030
is the perfect match for you.

361
00:22:00,310 --> 00:22:01,480
The marriage invitation has been sent.

362
00:22:02,160 --> 00:22:04,270
It’s settled then.

363
00:22:14,440 --> 00:22:16,480
Father, I won’t marry

364
00:22:16,590 --> 00:22:17,640
any woman in Daye

365
00:22:17,830 --> 00:22:18,960
but Shi Feixian.

366
00:22:19,270 --> 00:22:20,640
When is it your turn

367
00:22:21,270 --> 00:22:23,790
to decide on the royal marriage?

368
00:22:24,920 --> 00:22:27,790
I have the final say
in any royal marriages!

369
00:22:36,070 --> 00:22:37,240
If I can’t marry Miss Shi,

370
00:22:38,070 --> 00:22:39,680
I’d rather spend
the rest of my life alone!

371
00:22:40,400 --> 00:22:41,160
Ridiculous!

372
00:22:44,640 --> 00:22:45,720
The imperial edict has been issued.

373
00:22:46,680 --> 00:22:47,720
No more discussion.

374
00:22:48,480 --> 00:22:49,640
Since you don’t want to discuss anymore,

375
00:22:50,030 --> 00:22:51,310
I have nothing else to say, Father.

376
00:22:52,440 --> 00:22:53,550
Please forgive me

377
00:22:53,960 --> 00:22:56,590
for not attending the wedding.

378
00:22:56,880 --> 00:22:57,750
You unfilial son!

379
00:23:01,270 --> 00:23:02,110
Guards!

380
00:23:03,790 --> 00:23:04,480
Yes!

381
00:23:04,920 --> 00:23:06,590
Put him under house arrest.

382
00:23:06,790 --> 00:23:08,160
Without my decree,

383
00:23:09,350 --> 00:23:10,720
he mustn’t go out.

384
00:23:10,720 --> 00:23:11,400
Yes!

385
00:23:14,440 --> 00:23:15,070
Your Majesty.

386
00:23:20,400 --> 00:23:22,030
How could he not understand?

387
00:23:23,480 --> 00:23:27,070
The eldest daughter of Shi Jin
has married the Crown Prince.

388
00:23:28,440 --> 00:23:31,070
If her sister married the Second Prince,

389
00:23:32,750 --> 00:23:35,790
the Shi family will become too powerful

390
00:23:35,830 --> 00:23:37,110
and be a threat to me.

391
00:23:42,720 --> 00:23:43,920
Have you heard

392
00:23:44,030 --> 00:23:45,400
the latest news
from the imperial palace?

393
00:23:45,590 --> 00:23:47,110
Because the Second Prince

394
00:23:47,440 --> 00:23:49,110
didn’t agree to marry Xie Wanyu…

395
00:23:49,110 --> 00:23:49,640
Have a taste.

396
00:23:49,640 --> 00:23:50,920
…His Majesty gave him a slap.

397
00:23:50,920 --> 00:23:51,550
Really?

398
00:23:52,200 --> 00:23:55,000
Don’t tell anyone about it.

399
00:23:55,160 --> 00:23:56,160
I won’t.

400
00:23:56,310 --> 00:23:57,750
I promise with my cabbage.

401
00:23:58,030 --> 00:23:58,680
I won’t tell anyone.

402
00:23:58,680 --> 00:23:59,270
Okay.

403
00:24:01,720 --> 00:24:02,750
Have you heard that

404
00:24:02,750 --> 00:24:04,790
His Majesty wanted the Second Prince
to marry Xie Wanyu,

405
00:24:04,790 --> 00:24:06,590
but the two of them got into a fight?

406
00:24:06,640 --> 00:24:07,350
Really?

407
00:24:07,350 --> 00:24:09,240
Don’t tell anyone about it.

408
00:24:09,440 --> 00:24:11,880
If you do that,
you may be sentenced to death.

409
00:24:11,880 --> 00:24:13,790
Rest assured. I promise with my tofu.

410
00:24:14,140 --> 00:24:14,880
I won’t tell anyone.

411
00:24:16,200 --> 00:24:17,030
Big news!

412
00:24:17,030 --> 00:24:19,480
The Second Prince hit His Majesty
just because he didn’t want to

413
00:24:19,480 --> 00:24:20,350
marry Xie Wanyu.

414
00:24:20,350 --> 00:24:21,200
Are you serious?

415
00:24:21,350 --> 00:24:22,960
Don’t tell anyone about…

416
00:24:22,960 --> 00:24:25,590
Oh my goodness, there’s a revolt!

417
00:24:25,750 --> 00:24:28,480
The Second Prince refused to
marry Xie Wanyu

418
00:24:28,480 --> 00:24:30,830
and knocked His Majesty unconscious!

419
00:24:30,830 --> 00:24:32,830
Who told you that?

420
00:24:33,000 --> 00:24:33,720
It’s her!

421
00:24:33,830 --> 00:24:34,790
It’s her!

422
00:24:34,790 --> 00:24:35,830
No! It’s her!

423
00:24:35,960 --> 00:24:37,270
-Who on earth is it?
-It’s her!

424
00:24:37,790 --> 00:24:38,790
How could you say that out?

425
00:24:38,790 --> 00:24:39,680
That’s about His Majesty!

426
00:24:39,830 --> 00:24:40,510
Don’t go!

427
00:24:40,510 --> 00:24:41,350
It’s her!

428
00:24:42,880 --> 00:24:43,400
Young Master!

429
00:24:44,030 --> 00:24:45,960
Bodhisattva, please bless that
Young Master is safe.

430
00:24:47,790 --> 00:24:48,480
Du Jiu,

431
00:24:49,480 --> 00:24:51,030
I heard that if a drowned person

432
00:24:51,350 --> 00:24:52,480
falls into a coma,

433
00:24:52,640 --> 00:24:54,550
oxygen will be needed to save him.

434
00:24:59,310 --> 00:25:00,240
Thank you, Bodhisattva,

435
00:25:00,240 --> 00:25:01,790
for bringing Young Master back to life.

436
00:25:02,310 --> 00:25:03,400
Don’t thank Bodhisattva.

437
00:25:03,720 --> 00:25:05,590
The one who saved him is her.

438
00:25:07,270 --> 00:25:08,200
If it wasn’t for her,

439
00:25:08,400 --> 00:25:09,720
Young Master wouldn’t even
be in the water.

440
00:25:11,590 --> 00:25:12,240
Thank…

441
00:25:14,400 --> 00:25:15,790
Thank you for saving me, Baroness.

442
00:25:17,720 --> 00:25:18,830
As long as you’re fine.

443
00:25:19,640 --> 00:25:20,270
Young Master.

444
00:25:22,590 --> 00:25:23,400
I’m okay.

445
00:25:26,750 --> 00:25:27,590
Du Jiu.

446
00:25:28,030 --> 00:25:28,680
Young Master.

447
00:25:28,790 --> 00:25:29,640
Bring my…

448
00:25:31,240 --> 00:25:32,070
my overcoat.

449
00:25:32,270 --> 00:25:32,720
Okay.

450
00:25:37,310 --> 00:25:38,030
Young Master.

451
00:25:44,270 --> 00:25:45,000
Young Master?

452
00:25:52,160 --> 00:25:55,160
Count Cheng’an, you should put it on.

453
00:25:55,590 --> 00:25:58,720
I can’t repay you for saving me…

454
00:25:59,640 --> 00:26:02,830
But I can stop you from catching a cold.

455
00:26:07,240 --> 00:26:08,440
Thank you then, Count.

456
00:26:12,110 --> 00:26:13,440
This bookworm

457
00:26:13,790 --> 00:26:15,440
is not as boring as I thought.

458
00:26:18,640 --> 00:26:19,400
What?

459
00:26:20,790 --> 00:26:21,920
How come?

460
00:26:22,160 --> 00:26:22,960
Miss,

461
00:26:23,400 --> 00:26:24,750
though Count Cheng’an
isn’t good at skating,

462
00:26:24,750 --> 00:26:26,310
under Baroness Ban’s patient guidance,

463
00:26:26,310 --> 00:26:28,030
the two of them had a really good time

464
00:26:28,240 --> 00:26:29,070
on the ice.

465
00:26:30,640 --> 00:26:32,550
I see. You may leave.

466
00:26:33,400 --> 00:26:34,030
Yes.

467
00:26:42,830 --> 00:26:44,160
It’s so hot!

468
00:26:44,200 --> 00:26:45,400
Hold it, dear.

469
00:26:46,160 --> 00:26:47,640
Once the chill is pushed out
of your body,

470
00:26:47,640 --> 00:26:48,400
you’ll be all right.

471
00:26:48,400 --> 00:26:49,350
Yeah, that’s right.

472
00:26:58,160 --> 00:26:59,590
Why are you all staring at me?

473
00:27:02,240 --> 00:27:03,070
How is it

474
00:27:03,640 --> 00:27:04,590
going

475
00:27:05,030 --> 00:27:06,110
between Count Cheng’an and you?

476
00:27:08,510 --> 00:27:09,790
What’re you talking about?

477
00:27:12,030 --> 00:27:13,070
According to my plan,

478
00:27:13,310 --> 00:27:15,720
you’re his savior right now.

479
00:27:15,830 --> 00:27:17,640
And according to the script,

480
00:27:17,830 --> 00:27:20,000
he’s going to marry you to repay you.

481
00:27:21,000 --> 00:27:23,440
Was the accident set by you?

482
00:27:23,550 --> 00:27:25,030
What if he died?

483
00:27:25,030 --> 00:27:25,680
Wait a minute.

484
00:27:25,920 --> 00:27:27,510
I only set the skating activity.

485
00:27:27,640 --> 00:27:29,240
The accident has nothing to do with me.

486
00:27:29,440 --> 00:27:30,240
Don’t blame me.

487
00:27:30,400 --> 00:27:32,000
After all,

488
00:27:32,640 --> 00:27:35,200
you saved his life.

489
00:27:35,640 --> 00:27:37,880
He owes you now.

490
00:28:06,110 --> 00:28:07,920
Young Master, please dry yourself.

491
00:28:08,070 --> 00:28:08,960
Or you might catch a cold.

492
00:28:10,750 --> 00:28:11,440
I’m okay.

493
00:28:21,590 --> 00:28:22,750
His Majesty has arranged

494
00:28:22,830 --> 00:28:24,790
the marriage between the Second Prince
and Miss Xie.

495
00:28:26,270 --> 00:28:27,240
Have you got

496
00:28:27,790 --> 00:28:29,110
any clues to my mother’s bracelet?

497
00:28:29,270 --> 00:28:30,200
Everything’s ready.

498
00:28:30,400 --> 00:28:32,270
When the time is right,
we’ll sneak into Xie’s Mansion.

499
00:28:33,030 --> 00:28:33,960
Do it early.

500
00:28:45,830 --> 00:28:46,550
Young Master.

501
00:28:47,590 --> 00:28:50,590
What’s the number, Young Master?

502
00:28:52,270 --> 00:28:54,960
Young Master? Young Master.

503
00:28:55,000 --> 00:28:55,720
Look here.

504
00:28:56,720 --> 00:28:58,160
Why have I never seen

505
00:28:58,240 --> 00:28:59,590
this assistant before?

506
00:28:59,790 --> 00:29:02,030
You have a good eye, Young Master.

507
00:29:04,110 --> 00:29:04,960
This guy

508
00:29:05,240 --> 00:29:08,030
was entrusted to me by
my senior in the east of the city.

509
00:29:08,200 --> 00:29:09,440
He’s new in the business.

510
00:29:09,640 --> 00:29:10,880
I have a lot to teach him.

511
00:29:10,880 --> 00:29:12,240
Why do you cover your face?

512
00:29:12,920 --> 00:29:13,720
For fear of infection.

513
00:29:14,510 --> 00:29:16,000
I’m blind,

514
00:29:16,000 --> 00:29:17,270
but I didn’t catch a plague!

515
00:29:17,790 --> 00:29:18,790
Please calm down.

516
00:29:18,920 --> 00:29:19,920
I caught a cold,

517
00:29:20,000 --> 00:29:21,200
and I fear you might get infected.

518
00:29:26,790 --> 00:29:27,480
Physician.

519
00:29:29,400 --> 00:29:30,160
Tell me,

520
00:29:31,880 --> 00:29:34,070
is there any hope for my recovery?

521
00:29:37,440 --> 00:29:39,110
Forget it. You don’t need to answer me.

522
00:29:39,880 --> 00:29:40,830
Don’t be sad.

523
00:29:41,110 --> 00:29:42,350
Look on the bright side.

524
00:29:43,000 --> 00:29:43,790
For example,

525
00:29:44,270 --> 00:29:45,510
if you go hunting,

526
00:29:45,640 --> 00:29:46,680
you’ll be better than others for sure.

527
00:29:47,440 --> 00:29:49,030
You don’t even need to
close your left eye.

528
00:29:49,510 --> 00:29:50,350
How handy that is!

529
00:29:51,750 --> 00:29:53,030
What are you laughing about?

530
00:29:53,200 --> 00:29:54,440
What nonsense are you talking about?

531
00:29:55,920 --> 00:29:57,400
Please don’t be angry, Young Master.

532
00:29:57,680 --> 00:29:59,720
He’s just young and garrulous.

533
00:30:00,030 --> 00:30:01,110
He didn’t mean it.

534
00:30:01,240 --> 00:30:02,920
Please forgive him.

535
00:30:03,160 --> 00:30:05,350
Hurry! Apologize! Apologize!

536
00:30:05,480 --> 00:30:06,110
I’m sorry.

537
00:30:06,110 --> 00:30:06,960
Get lost!

538
00:30:07,750 --> 00:30:08,720
Yes, I will.

539
00:30:08,720 --> 00:30:09,440
-I will get lost.
-Go. Just go.

540
00:30:11,310 --> 00:30:12,070
I’m so pissed off.

541
00:30:12,440 --> 00:30:14,830
Please don’t be. Please don’t be.

542
00:30:39,030 --> 00:30:39,720
Young Master.

543
00:30:39,750 --> 00:30:40,830
What’s going on outside?

544
00:30:41,000 --> 00:30:42,750
People from the Ban family are here.

545
00:30:42,920 --> 00:30:43,920
Baroness Ban is here?

546
00:30:57,920 --> 00:30:58,960
Don’t let her in.

547
00:30:59,790 --> 00:31:00,680
Why?

548
00:31:00,960 --> 00:31:02,680
Baroness Ban is here to see you.

549
00:31:05,790 --> 00:31:06,550
No.

550
00:31:11,000 --> 00:31:11,640
Uncle Rong,

551
00:31:12,480 --> 00:31:13,790
if she asks the reason,

552
00:31:14,310 --> 00:31:15,480
just tell her that I’m sick

553
00:31:15,750 --> 00:31:16,680
and it’s not convenient to see her.

554
00:31:17,350 --> 00:31:19,240
You don’t want to see her, Young Master?

555
00:31:23,350 --> 00:31:24,000
Not that.

556
00:31:25,510 --> 00:31:26,720
So, you want to see her.

557
00:31:27,310 --> 00:31:28,070
Uncle Rong.

558
00:31:29,720 --> 00:31:30,750
I can’t see her.

559
