00:43:03,400 --> 00:43:05,550
My love for Hua is witnessed
by the sun and the moon!

830
00:43:05,550 --> 00:43:06,280
Get away!

831
00:43:07,800 --> 00:43:08,440
Marquis!

832
00:43:10,800 --> 00:43:12,070
The sun and the moon…!

833
00:43:12,070 --> 00:43:12,800
-Get away!
-Marquis!

834
00:43:13,320 --> 00:43:15,840
I’m really scared of him.

835
00:43:17,710 --> 00:43:19,030
How ridiculous.

836
00:43:19,800 --> 00:43:20,510
Yeah.

837
00:43:20,760 --> 00:43:21,480
Your Majesty.

838
00:43:22,000 --> 00:43:25,150
That’s why I can’t eat

839
00:43:25,150 --> 00:43:26,030
or sleep well lately.

840
00:43:26,030 --> 00:43:28,480
Look, even my belly got smaller.

841
00:43:29,880 --> 00:43:32,190
Count Cheng’an asks to see Your Majesty.

842
00:43:32,510 --> 00:43:33,190
Grant.

843
00:43:36,800 --> 00:43:37,670
Your Majesty.

844
00:43:38,840 --> 00:43:40,000
You came at the right time.

845
00:43:40,510 --> 00:43:42,550
Have you heard of
what happened to Baroness Ban?

846
00:43:43,000 --> 00:43:43,800
Yes, kind of.

847
00:43:44,440 --> 00:43:46,190
Baroness Ban was born in a rich family

848
00:43:46,630 --> 00:43:48,440
yet she can understand the bitterness
of the poor scholars

849
00:43:48,510 --> 00:43:50,190
and have faith in their future.

850
00:43:50,280 --> 00:43:52,480
I admire her for that.

851
00:43:53,000 --> 00:43:55,630
And I can understand the guy
who’s infatuated with her.

852
00:43:56,400 --> 00:43:58,840
But as for the way out,

853
00:43:58,840 --> 00:44:01,440
I’m afraid only Baroness Ban
can figure out.

854
00:44:02,150 --> 00:44:03,510
Isn’t he sick?

855
00:44:03,920 --> 00:44:05,800
But he doesn’t look like that.

856
00:44:06,280 --> 00:44:08,030
Count Cheng’an is right.

857
00:44:08,630 --> 00:44:10,110
The love affair

858
00:44:10,630 --> 00:44:12,110
is out of my power.

859
00:44:13,320 --> 00:44:15,960
Let her figure it out by herself.

860
00:44:16,880 --> 00:44:17,760
Ban Huai.

861
00:44:19,440 --> 00:44:21,320
Yes, Your Majesty.

862
00:44:23,590 --> 00:44:25,920
I shouldn’t have brought this up.

863
00:44:31,510 --> 00:44:33,760
What? He’s not sick?

864
00:44:34,960 --> 00:44:38,070
I was talking with His Majesty.

865
00:44:38,550 --> 00:44:39,880
Then he came in.

866
00:44:40,230 --> 00:44:43,280
He doesn’t seem sick at all.

867
00:44:43,590 --> 00:44:45,070
Count Cheng’an, how dare you

868
00:44:45,110 --> 00:44:46,320
trick me!

869
00:44:46,710 --> 00:44:48,510
That bookworm wants to

870
00:44:48,590 --> 00:44:49,670
suffer more from me?

871
00:44:50,440 --> 00:44:52,840
Ban Hua, there’s one waiting outside.

872
00:44:54,150 --> 00:44:55,110
He’s still there?

873
00:44:56,000 --> 00:44:57,030
How about giving him a chance?

874
00:44:58,230 --> 00:45:00,840
He wants to force you to marry him.
That’s ridiculous!

875
00:45:01,280 --> 00:45:01,960
Drive him away!

876
00:45:02,150 --> 00:45:02,920
Hold it.

877
00:45:05,760 --> 00:45:08,230
Easy, dear. Let him wait.

878
00:45:09,000 --> 00:45:12,320
Let’s see how many days
he can wait there.

879
00:45:17,230 --> 00:45:18,880
My beauty is to blame.

